#

Kefir Chia Pudding

10 min
$3.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyNuts (if using)

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh ProteinLow Sugar

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastSnackHealthy

Description

A creamy and nutritious pudding made with kefir and chia seeds, perfect for a refreshing breakfast or snack.

Ingredients

  • kefir: 1 cup
  • chia seeds: 1/4 cup
  • honey or maple syrup: 1-2 tablespoons
  • vanilla extract: 1 teaspoon
  • fresh fruits (berries, banana, etc.): 1/2 cup
  • nuts or seeds (optional): 2 tablespoons
